$P\vee Q$


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}


|$P$ |$Q$ |$P \vee Q$ |
|:---|:---|:----------|
|T   |T   |T          |
|T   |F   |T          |
|F   |T   |T          |
|F   |F   |F          |


:::
:::


$\neg P$


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}


|$P$ |$\neg P$ |
|:---|:--------|
|T   |F        |
|F   |T        |


:::
:::


$P \rightarrow Q$


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}


|$P$ |$Q$ |$P \rightarrow Q$ |
|:---|:---|:-----------------|
|T   |T   |T                 |
|T   |F   |F                 |
|F   |T   |T                 |
|F   |F   |T                 |


:::
:::


$P\leftrightarrow Q$


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}


|$P$ |$Q$ |$P \leftrightarrow Q$ |
|:---|:---|:---------------------|
|T   |T   |T                     |
|T   |F   |F                     |
|F   |T   |F                     |
|F   |F   |T                     |


:::
:::


